# {{projectName}}

A multi-agent X Space team powered by [xspace-agent](https://github.com/xspace-agent/xspace-agent).

This template creates a team of two agents — a **host** and an **expert** — that collaborate in an X Space using round-robin turn management.

## Setup

1. Fill in your API keys in `.env`
2. Run the team:

```bash
npm start -- https://x.com/i/spaces/YOUR_SPACE_ID
```

## Customization

Edit `src/index.{{#if typescript}}ts{{else}}js{{/if}}` to:

- Add more agents to the `agents` array
- Change the turn management strategy (`queue`, `round-robin`, `director`)
- Customize each agent's system prompt and personality
